{"word":"G497 - ἀντιστρατεύομαι - antistrateúomai - an-tee-strat-yoo'-om-ahee - War against","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀντιστρατεύομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">antistrateúomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-tee-strat-yoo'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">War against</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விரோதமாய் போராடு"},{"paragraph":"1. to make a military expedition, or take the field, against anyone"},{"paragraph":"2. to oppose, war against"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G473 - ἀντί - antí - an-tee'/473\">G473</a> and <a href=\"#/G4754 - στρατεύομαι - strateúomai - strat-yoo'-om-ahee/4754\">G4754</a>; (figuratively) to <i>attack</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>destroy:</i> - war against.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}